#: templates/gnome/information.html:49
msgid ""
"Donations are used to fund developers to work on under-resourced parts of "
"GNOME as part of our <a href=\"https://fellowship.gnome.org/\">Fellowship "
"Program</a>"
msgstr ""
"Donacije se uporabljajo za financiranje razvijalcev, ki delajo na premalo "
"financiranih delih GNOME v okviru <a href=\"https://fellowship.gnome.org/"
